    "introduction": "Two-time Emmy® Award winner Dana Delany, four-time Emmy® Award winner Doris Roberts, Megan Gallagher (“Blind Obsession”) and Oscar® and Golden Globe winner Louise Fletcher combine their considerable talents in “A Time to Remember,” a powerful drama about a daughter torn between past and future and a mother on the brink of losing both.In “A Time to Remember,” Delany and Roberts portray Britt Calhoun, a gifted artist with an infant son struggling to prove her independence and self-worth and Maggie Calhoun, an iron-willed matriarch struggling to maintain control of her family – and herself – as she faces the frightening early symptoms of Alzheimer’s disease.As the family assembles for the Thanksgiving holiday, years of unresolved conflict surface, along with the silent and relentless threat from Alzheimer’s. Under the shadow of the illness that is destined to separate their minds, Britt and Maggie form the fragile beginnings of an unbreakable bond of the heart.",
